# Installation

> pip install p3ui
> 

# Hello World

```python
from p3ui import *


async def main():
    window = Window(title='Hello World!')
    
    window.user_interface.content = Row(
        justify_content=Justification.SpaceAround,
        align_items=Alignment.Center,
        children=[Text('Hello'), Text('World')])
    
    await window.closed

    
run(main())
```
